And Zhao Mingxuan as well.

202
00:11:04,121 --> 00:11:05,161
Do you think he's still

203
00:11:05,281 --> 00:11:06,321
the same brother that he used to be?

204
00:11:06,721 --> 00:11:07,761
No way.

205
00:11:08,481 --> 00:11:09,921
