Fine.

212
00:11:23,441 --> 00:11:25,041
I don't come near you all.

213
00:11:25,401 --> 00:11:26,561
That's the biggest help.

214
00:11:31,121 --> 00:11:31,961
Where are you going?

215
00:11:33,081 --> 00:11:33,921
Wusu.

216
00:11:43,042 --> 00:11:45,603
(Wusu Radio & TV Group)

217
00:12:05,401 --> 00:12:06,161
